{"word":"ὡμαλία","slug":"ὡμαλία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n116173\" key=\"w(mali/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὡμᾰλία</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n116173.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">flat rate, average,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐγδίδομεν . . τὰς μὲν στήλας . . πρὸς λίθον ἐφ᾽ ὡμαλίαν ὅ τι ἂν εὕρωσιν</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.3073.7</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (Lebad., <date TEIform=\"date\">ii B. C.</date>); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">συντελέσει διάχωμα μῆκος ἐφ᾽ ὡμαλίαν ε̄, πλάτος κάτω ξ̄ ἄνω μ̄, ὥστ᾽ εἶναι ἐφ᾽ ὡμαλίαν ν̄</quote_> <bibl n=\"http://www.trismegistos.org/text/78721\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PPetr.\">PPetr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3p.125</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <date TEIform=\"date\">(iii B. C.)</date>. (Formed fr. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀν-ωμαλία,</foreign> cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὁμαλός.</foreign>)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}